				.row
					.about-video-section__main.col-12.col-md
						.about-video-section__title(data-aos="fade-up") Our team consists of practitioners who have 15 years of experience in launching and managing projects. <br> worked with a wide array of clients across the globe to <br> apply design fundamentals of elegance, simplicity
						.row.align-items-end
							.col-4.col-md-5.col-xl-4(data-aos="fade-up")
								+arrow-link('About us', URLS.pages.about, 'about-video-section__more')
							.col-8.col-md-7.col-xl-8(data-aos="fade-up")
								.about-video-section__text We make our customers ' products valuable in the eyes of customers. To do this, we analyze and study people, build long-term strategies for interacting with them, develop creative ideas and create a bright design. We use all opportunities to solve business problems.

					.about-video-section__aside.col-12.col-md.order-first.order-md-0(data-aos="fade-up")
